{"id":128319,"type":6,"name":"法门寺猜想","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1c/79/128319_nWLAR.jpg","summary":"　　《法门寺猜想》讲了一对恋人的三世情缘。唐朝的元公主与法门寺的小和尚觉能相恋，后来觉能知道自己是被掉包的皇子，而公主是宰相的女儿。觉能后为保护佛骨自焚而亡。公主也自刎了。第二世是一个卖茶的缘妹和一个金银匠阜能的故事。两人相恋，但缘妹被外族拓跋氏看上，阜能为了国家，也为了缘妹，只得远征拓跋。第三世主持人元缘和年轻的历史学家小唐在挖掘法门寺时相识。小唐写了《法门寺猜想》的剧本给元缘，元缘后来才明白自己也许就是元公主和缘妹的前世今生，当他要去找小唐时，小唐已经出家，法名可能，远走。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>法门寺猜想</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/17127\">袁立</a> / 周里京 / 王涛 / 沈琳</li><li><span>集数: </span>16</li><li><span>开始: </span>1997</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 爱情 / 科幻 / 历史</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>导演: </span>陈家林</li><li><span>编剧: </span>杨捷</li>","eps":[{"id":502758,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502758","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502759,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502759","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502760,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502760","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502761,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502761","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502762,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502762","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502763,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502763","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502764,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502764","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502765,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502765","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":502766,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/502766","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"de